      "id": "30d600583ad1",
      "name": "qwen-skill-derin-dogrulama",
      "prompt": "Saat $(date '+%H:%M'). Skill derin do\u011frulama oturumu.\n\n\u0130lk ad\u0131m: ~/.hermes/scripts/.verify_ilerleme dosyas\u0131n\u0131 kontrol et. Yoksa olu\u015ftur: \"0\" yaz.\n\u0130\u00e7indeki say\u0131y\u0131 oku (N). Bu, do\u011frulanacak s\u0131radaki skill index'i.\n\n\u0130kinci ad\u0131m: Skill listesini al:\nls -d ~/.hermes/skills/security/*/\nBu listeyi s\u0131rala, N. s\u0131radaki skill'i se\u00e7.\n\n\u00dc\u00e7\u00fcnc\u00fc ad\u0131m: Skill i\u00e7eri\u011fini oku:\n- SKILL.md'den ba\u015fl\u0131k ve \u00f6zet\n- references/qwen_yanit.txt (varsa)\n- references/diyalog.txt (varsa)\n- references/qwen_yanit_dogrulanmis.txt (varsa)\n\nD\u00f6rd\u00fcnc\u00fc ad\u0131m: Bu skill'deki t\u00fcm bilgileri qwen2.5-coder'a g\u00f6ndererek DER\u0130NLEMES\u0130NE do\u011frulat:\ncurl -s --max-time 180 -X POST http://localhost:11434/api/generate -d '{\"model\":\"qwen2.5-coder:7b\",\"prompt\":\"\u015eu konuyu detayl\u0131 do\u011frula. Do\u011fru/yanl\u0131\u015f her noktay\u0131 belirt. Yanl\u0131\u015f varsa d\u00fczelt: [KONU BASLIGI + ICERIK]\",\"stream\":false}'\n\nBe\u015finci ad\u0131m: Sonucu skill dizinine kaydet:\necho \"DOGRULAMA $(date): [sonuc]\" > ~/.hermes/skills/security/[SKILL_ADI]/references/qwen_derin_dogrulama.txt\n\nAlt\u0131nc\u0131 ad\u0131m: \u0130lerleme dosyas\u0131n\u0131 g\u00fcncelle (N+1 yaz).\n\nYedinci ad\u0131m: Telegram'a k\u0131sa rapor g\u00f6nder:\n\"[SKILL_ADI] derin do\u011frulama tamam. S\u0131radaki: [sonraki_skill]\"\n\nE\u011fer t\u00fcm skill'ler bittiyle (index > toplam skill say\u0131s\u0131), \"T\u00dcM SKILL'LER DO\u011eRULANDI \u2705\" yaz ve dur.",
